Her tenure at Fannie Mae has been long, since 1994.
The vice chairwoman of the RAND Corp. board of trustees and former secretary of labor under President Ronald Reagan, Korologos must now oversee the investigation of Fannie Mae's accounting practices, governance and structure and executive compensation.
But Korologos' other affiliations show links to Fannie Mae.
