The fifth book in the series, "Harry Potter and the Order of the Phoenix", published in June last year, received 420000 advance orders after the announcement of its publication.
British publisher Bloomsbury said Tuesday that Rowling, pregnant with her third child, had finished the latest and penultimate book in the series about the teenage wizard's adventures, and it will be published on July 16 next year.
The books have captivated millions of children and adults and spawned a multi million dollar film, merchandising and publication industry.
The sixth book in the hugely successful Harry Potter series, 'Harry Potter and the Half Blood Prince', will be published on July 16 next year, its publisher said Tuesday.
British publisher Bloomsbury said J.K. Rowling had finished the latest and penultimate book in the series about the teenage wizard's adventures that has captivated millions of childrens and adult and spawned a multi million dollar film, merchandising and pulication industry.
